<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Am</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.    Am             Dm
 Araılap atty tańdarym,
.   E7          Am
 Nuryńa meni bólediń.
.   Am          Dm
 Táńirim Isa, qanyńmen,
.  E7             Am
 Kúnámniń qunyn ótediń.

[C1]
.    A               Dm
   Qınaldyń Isa men úshin,
.    G                C
   Aıqyshqa berip tánińdi,
.     Am             Dm
   Qutqaryp aldyń kúnádan,
.    E7         Am
   Álemdi jáne elimdi.

[V2]
 Shydadyń Iem, men úshin,
 Janyńdy salyp azapqa,
 Adamnyń árbir urpaǵy
 Barmaıdy sense tozaqqa.

[V3]
 Keýdeńnen qanyń tógildi,
 Tamshylap jerge toqtalmaı,
 Kúnásiz Isa kerildi,
 Aıqyshtan baqyt tapqandaı.

[V4]
 Kúnáni endi jasama,
 Kıeli Isa qany úshin,
 Táýbege kelshi baýyrym,
 Ómirdiń uǵyp mánin shyn.</lyrics>
<title>Araılap atty tańdarym РӘЖ136 Қак35</title>
<author>Malaev Sábıt, Qyzylbórikov Bolat</author>
